<html lang="zh-Hant-TW">
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="content-type">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>生活照片介紹</title>
    <style>
   body {
          font-family: "微軟正黑體", sans-serif;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          background-image: url('../icon/Bg%20summer.jpg');
          background-size: cover;
          background-position: center;
          background-repeat: no-repeat;
          background-attachment: fixed;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
          min-height: 100vh;
        }
    header {
      background-color: #ff7043;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .photo-block {
      max-width: 800px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .photo-block img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }
    .photo-block p {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 15px;
      font-size: 18px;
      background-color: #fff3e0;
    }
    footer {
      background-color: #eee;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>702 生活照片介紹</header>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="photo-block"> <img src="../pic/S2.JPG" alt="生活照片">
        <p>與同學在戶外的開心合照 ─ 記錄我們的青春笑容</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <footer>製作：702 團隊｜青春的每一刻都值得紀錄<br>
      &nbsp;<a href="../../../index.html"><img style="width: 195px; height: 107px;"
          alt="" src="../icon/back%20home%20summer.png"></a><br>
      <a href="../../spring/girls/girls.html"><img style="width: 141px; height: 63px;"
          src="../icon/last%20page%20summer.png"></a><a href="../school%20pictures/school_picture.html"><img
          style="width: 165px; height: 56px;" src="../icon/next%20page%20summer.png"></a><br>
      <a href="../../spring/boys/boys.html"><img style="width: 123px; height: 73px;"
          src="../icon/last%20season%20summer.png"></a><a href="../../Autumn/teacher/teacher.html"><img
          style="width: 122px; height: 72px;" src="../icon/next%20season%20summer.png"></a></footer>
  </body>
</html>
